Here you can find a cross-development system for micro-BESM project,
based on Portable C Compiler from Unix V7.

It includes:

  * as          - assembler and disassembler
  * ld          - linker, archiver, and other object file utilities
  * lib         - library for long and unsigned arithmetics
  * mip, pcc    - Johnson's portable C compiler
  * cc          - compiler front end
  * microbesm   - include files

To build and install to /usr/local/bin, run:

    make
    make install
